{"word":"ἠλίθιος","slug":"ἠλίθιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἠλίθιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἤλιθα'><el>ἤλιθα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>idle, vain, random</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of persons, <i>stupid, foolish, silly</i>, like <el>μάταιος</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ίως</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <el>ἠλίθιον</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}